## Next Steps

* **Working Group Last Calls (WGLC)**: The chairs plan to initiate WGLCs for both [draft-ietf-radext-deprecating-radius](https://datatracker.ietf.org/id/draft-ietf-radext-deprecating-radius) and [draft-ietf-radext-review-radius](https://datatracker.ietf.org/id/draft-ietf-radext-review-radius) shortly after the August updates are published.
* **Rechartering**: The new charter is expected to be approved by the IAB by mid-August. Once approved, the chairs will formally adopt the Connect-Info draft and outstanding Cisco/Sri drafts.
* **Protocol Interoperability**: Live testing of the Protocol-Error specifications is scheduled for August, with results to be shared before IETF 121.